videos.description: Trey Landers comes up with a steal and finishes in transition with a finger-roll layup as Dayton is up early on Rhode Island.
videos.headline: Landers gets steal and score for Dayton

videos.description: Trey Landers times up the jump and rejects a shot into the stands for Dayton.
videos.headline: Landers skies for the huge block

videos.description: Kostas Antetokounmpo, younger brother of the Bucks' star, goes up and gets the high alley-oop pass and finishes with a slam.
videos.headline: Dayton's Antetokounmpo with shades of Giannis on the alley-oop

videos.description: Jeff Dowtin gets into the lane and hits the floater for the Rams.
videos.headline: Dowtin floats and scores for Rhode Island

videos.description: E.C. Matthews drains a 3-pointer as Rhode Island breaks open the lead against Dayton.
videos.headline: Matthews caps off URI run with a step-back triple

videos.description: Jared Terrell knocks down a 3-pointer and then picks up the steal on the next possession for Rhode Island.
videos.headline: Terrell sparks URI on back-to-back possessions
